{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.920", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich prinzipiell, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.560", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich die Erkenntnis durchsetzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.960", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Befristungen unbedingt begrenzt werden m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.440", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass vielen Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.160", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die jetzt darunter leiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie ihren Lebensplan nicht so gestalten k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.080", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie das wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.840", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie keine Familien gr\u00fcnden oder keine Wohnung kaufen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.680", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie oftmals keinen Kredit bekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "geholfen wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.120", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "besser planen zu k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele f\u00fchlen sich als Menschen zweiter Klasse. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.840", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben Angst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob ihr Vertrag verl\u00e4ngert wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.640", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie engagieren sich selten f\u00fcr den Betriebsrat und leisten oftmals unbezahlte Mehrarbeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.640", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es kann und darf nicht sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Besch\u00e4ftigte \u00fcber Jahre hinweg von einer Befristung in die n\u00e4chste stolpern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.080", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es darf nicht sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.760", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Unsicherheit endlos ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.280", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt lese ich in Ihrem Entwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie die Kettenbefristung reduzieren m\u00f6chten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.440", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Handwerklich ist er\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.560", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich m\u00f6chte das sch\u00f6n ausdr\u00fccken\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.080", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht gut gemacht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.920", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kommen auch leider viel zu sp\u00e4t; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn in den Koalitionsverhandlungen haben wir verabredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.600", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es k\u00fcnftig keine Befristungen mehr geben kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.120", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man mit demselben Arbeitgeber vorher ein unbefristetes Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnis abgeschlossen hatte oder bereits ein oder mehrere Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnisse\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.040", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis zu einer Gesamtdauer von f\u00fcnf Jahren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vorlagen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.160", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben das schon \u00f6fters geh\u00f6rt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.680", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese H\u00f6chstdauer erstrecken wir auch auf vorherige Entleihungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.320", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir nehmen also auch die Leiharbeiter in diese Regelung hinein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.360", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ganz wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Meilenstein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.640", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein erneutes befristetes Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnis mit demselben Arbeitgeber ist dann erst nach drei Jahren wieder m\u00f6glich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.440", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach einem unbefristeten Arbeitsverh\u00e4ltnis kann kein befristeter Vertrag mehr abgeschlossen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Riesenvorteil. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das umsetzen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.760", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schreiben in Ihrem Gesetzentwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.160", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man k\u00f6nne davon ausgehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch eine sachgrundlose Befristung immer vor dem Hintergrund einer betrieblichen \u00dcberlegung und daher aus sachlichem Grund erfolgt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.320", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das steht auf Seite\u00a06 Ihres Gesetzentwurfs. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So blau\u00e4ugig w\u00e4re ich diesbez\u00fcglich nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.800", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sehe das nicht so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Befristungen immer vor dem Hintergrund einer betrieblichen \u00dcberlegung und damit aus sachlichem Grund erfolgen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.840", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht in Ordnung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.960", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn ein Arbeitgeber das anspricht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.600", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mein Anspruch an die Politik ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.920", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Leitplanken setzen und sich Arbeitgeber und Arbeitnehmer innerhalb dieser Leitplanken gut bewegen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.360", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie damit gut fahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.360", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das IAB hat uns best\u00e4tigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.920", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir mit diesen im Koalitionsvertrag vorgesehenen \u00c4nderungen den gr\u00f6\u00dften Eingriff in das Befristungsrecht seit 1985 vornehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.600", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das nutzt 400\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.960", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "1985 bin ich selber als Jugendvertreter auf die Stra\u00dfe gegangen und habe gegen die von Helmut Kohl geplante Einf\u00fchrung der sachgrundlosen Befristung demonstriert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.160", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damals waren Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.560", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kleinw\u00e4chter\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen nichts daf\u00fcr\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "noch nicht geboren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden die H\u00f6chstdauer f\u00fcr sachgrundlose Befristungen von 24 auf 18\u00a0Monate verk\u00fcrzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.600", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insgesamt ist das ein wichtiger Meilenstein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.080", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber den wir in der SPD lange und gut diskutiert haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.240", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses Thema hat uns angetrieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in die Koalition zu gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.720", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.480", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das umsetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.680", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wird vielen Menschen in diesem Land helfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.520", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Weg in Richtung einer arbeitnehmerfreundlichen Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt leider nicht f\u00fcr Ihren Gesetzentwurf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.880", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der letzte Redner in der heutigen Debatte ist Max Straubinger von der CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich muss mich korrigieren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.760", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der letzte Redner vor Sonnenaufgang. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danach geht es weiter."
   ]
  }
 ]
}